title: Got Questions About Transferring to CSUN? Come Talk with the CSUN Peer Mentor on October ...
text: ( Source : Los Angeles Valley College ) The CSUN Peer Mentor will be on-campus to answer questions about transferring to Cal State Northridge on October 14 from 9 a.m.-1 p.m. at the Career / Transfer Center . The LAVC Career/Transfer Center ( CTC )
